transcript:

Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan sir ji koi wo nursery wala hai grass ka dealer Navsari ke nazdeek mein?
Customer: Kya cheez?
Customer: Hume jo ghaas garden hota hai na garden.
Executive: Hmm.
Customer: Grass ka dealer chahiye Navsari Gujarat mein hai koi?
Executive: Kis company se baat kar rahe hain sir aap?
Customer: Hum to
Executive: Aapke yahan package mera chalta hai.
Executive: Company ka naam bataiye sir.
Customer: Himalaya krishak parivar.
Executive: To aap jo hai IndiaMART ki directory pe jaate hue product search kijiye wahan pe related supplier aapko sare mil jayenge sir.
Customer: Achcha.
Executive: Haan ji.
Executive: Google pe jo aapko product chahiye na aap wo Google pe uska naam dalna IndiaMART ke link pe click karna sare suppliers ki contact detail samne aa jayegi.
Customer: Theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai sir.
